    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Hexo-GitHub-Pages-个人博客搭建与笔记管理终极指南"><a href="#Hexo-GitHub-Pages-个人博客搭建与笔记管理终极指南" class="headerlink" title="Hexo + GitHub Pages 个人博客搭建与笔记管理终极指南"></a><strong>Hexo + GitHub Pages 个人博客搭建与笔记管理终极指南</strong></h3><h4 id="一、核心概念"><a href="#一、核心概念" class="headerlink" title="一、核心概念"></a><strong>一、核心概念</strong></h4><ol><li><p><strong>Hexo</strong>：基于 Node.js 的静态博客框架，用 Markdown 写文章，生成 HTML 部署。</p></li><li><p><strong>GitHub Pages</strong>：免费托管静态网站的服务，自动关联 <code>用户名.github.io</code> 仓库。</p></li><li><p><strong>Markdown</strong>：轻量级标记语言，支持代码块、表格、图片等（文件扩展名 <code>.md</code>）。</p></li></ol><h4 id="二、完整工作流程"><a href="#二、完整工作流程" class="headerlink" title="二、完整工作流程"></a><strong>二、完整工作流程</strong></h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph LR</span><br><span class="line">  A[安装环境] --&gt; B[初始化Hexo]</span><br><span class="line">  B --&gt; C[配置主题/插件]</span><br><span class="line">  C --&gt; D[写Markdown笔记]</span><br><span class="line">  D --&gt; E[本地预览]</span><br><span class="line">  E --&gt; F[部署到GitHub]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="三、详细步骤分解"><a href="#三、详细步骤分解" class="headerlink" title="三、详细步骤分解"></a><strong>三、详细步骤分解</strong></h4><h5 id="1-环境准备"><a href="#1-环境准备" class="headerlink" title="1. 环境准备"></a><strong>1. 环境准备</strong></h5><ul><li><strong>安装工具</strong>：</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Node.js（&gt;=18.x）</span></span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Git</span></span><br><span class="line">git --version</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Hexo</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="2-项目初始化"><a href="#2-项目初始化" class="headerlink" title="2. 项目初始化"></a><strong>2. 项目初始化</strong></h5><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init my-blog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> my-blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="3-关键配置文件"><a href="#3-关键配置文件" class="headerlink" title="3. 关键配置文件"></a><strong>3. 关键配置文件</strong></h5><ul><li><strong><code>_config.yml</code>（根目录）</strong>：</li></ul><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">https://用户名.github.io/</span>   <span class="comment"># 或子路径如 /repo-name/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">root:</span> <span class="string">/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">butterfly</span>              <span class="comment"># 主题名</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:用户名/仓库名.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>主题配置</strong>（如 <code>themes/butterfly/_config.yml</code>）：</li></ul><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">首页:</span> <span class="string">/</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">归档:</span> <span class="string">/archives</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="4-笔记（文章）管理"><a href="#4-笔记（文章）管理" class="headerlink" title="4. 笔记（文章）管理"></a><strong>4. 笔记（文章）管理</strong></h5><ul><li><strong>创建新笔记</strong>：</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new <span class="string">&quot;Java多线程详解&quot;</span>  <span class="comment"># 生成 source/_posts/Java多线程详解.md</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>Markdown 模板</strong>：</li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Java多线程详解</span><br><span class="line">date: 2024-07-20</span><br><span class="line">tags: [Java, 并发]</span><br><span class="line">categories: 技术</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">cover: /images/cover.jpg  # 封面图</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 一、线程基础</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```java</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">public class ThreadDemo extends Thread &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    public void run() &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">        System.out.println(&quot;线程运行&quot;);</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="5-图片与资源"><a href="#5-图片与资源" class="headerlink" title="5. 图片与资源"></a><strong>5. 图片与资源</strong></h5><ul><li><p><strong>推荐方式</strong>：</p><ol><li>启用 <code>post_asset_folder</code>：</li></ol></li></ul><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># _config.yml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">post_asset_folder:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><pre><code>2.图片引用：</code></pre><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">描述</span>](<span class="link">文章标题/图片.jpg</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="6-本地调试与部署"><a href="#6-本地调试与部署" class="headerlink" title="6. 本地调试与部署"></a><strong>6. 本地调试与部署</strong></h5><ul><li><strong>实时预览</strong></li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server  <span class="comment"># 访问 http://localhost:4000</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><strong>生成并部署</strong>：</li></ul><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="四、常见问题解决方案"><a href="#四、常见问题解决方案" class="headerlink" title="四、常见问题解决方案"></a><strong>四、常见问题解决方案</strong></h4><table><thead><tr><th>问题现象</th><th>原因</th><th>解决方案</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>样式&#x2F;图片404</td><td><code>url</code> 或 <code>root</code> 配置错误</td><td>检查 <code>_config.yml</code> 路径，确保末尾有 <code>/</code></td></tr><tr><td>部署后无更新</td><td>GitHub 缓存</td><td>在仓库 Settings &gt; Pages 点重新部署</td></tr><tr><td>Markdown 表格渲染异常</td><td>语法错误</td><td>用 &#96;&#96;对齐列，例如：<br><code>| 列1 | 列2 |</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h4 id="五、效率工具推荐"><a href="#五、效率工具推荐" class="headerlink" title="五、效率工具推荐"></a><strong>五、效率工具推荐</strong></h4><ol><li><p><strong>写作工具</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>Typora（实时渲染 Markdown）</p></li><li><p>VS Code + Markdown All in One 插件</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>图床工具</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>PicGo（自动上传图片生成链接）</p></li><li><p>腾讯云 COS&#x2F;Aliyun OSS（付费但稳定）</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>SEO 优化</strong>：</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="六、高级技巧"><a href="#六、高级技巧" class="headerlink" title="六、高级技巧"></a><strong>六、高级技巧</strong></h4><ul><li><p><strong>自动化部署</strong>：通过 GitHub Actions 实现提交代码自动部署。</p></li><li><p><strong>CDN 加速</strong>：将静态资源托管到 jsDelivr。</p></li><li><p><strong>自定义域名</strong>：</p><ol><li><p>在 <code>source/CNAME</code> 写入域名（如 <code>blog.example.com</code>）。</p></li><li><p>DNS 解析添加 CNAME 记录指向 <code>用户名.github.io</code>。</p></li></ol></li></ul><h4 id="七、示例命令速查表"><a href="#七、示例命令速查表" class="headerlink" title="七、示例命令速查表"></a><strong>七、示例命令速查表</strong></h4><table><thead><tr><th>功能</th><th>命令</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>新建文章</td><td><code>hexo new &quot;标题&quot;</code></td></tr><tr><td>本地运行</td><td><code>hexo server</code></td></tr><tr><td>生成静态文件</td><td><code>hexo generate</code>（或 <code>hexo g</code>）</td></tr><tr><td>部署到 GitHub</td><td><code>hexo deploy</code>（或 <code>hexo d</code>）</td></tr><tr><td>清理缓存</td><td><code>hexo clean</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h4 id="八、总结"><a href="#八、总结" class="headerlink" title="八、总结"></a><strong>八、总结</strong></h4><ol><li><p><strong>写作流程</strong>：<br> <code>hexo new</code> → 编辑 Markdown → <code>hexo server</code> 调试 → <code>hexo deploy</code> 发布。</p></li><li><p><strong>内容管理</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>文章在 <code>source/_posts/</code></p></li><li><p>图片随文章存放或集中放 <code>source/images/</code>。</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>持续维护</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>定期备份 <code>source/</code> 文件夹。</p></li><li><p>通过 Git 管理博客源码（如推送到私有仓库）。</p></li></ul></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
